                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen production system combining solar energy and retired battery recycling",
                    "一种太阳能联合退役电池再利用的制氢系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen production system combining solar energy and retired battery recycling. The hydrogen production system comprises a solar power supply system, a classified electrolytic cell and a hydrogen storage module, the solar power supply system comprises a solar photovoltaic cell module, the solar photovoltaic cell module is connected with a voltage stabilization control module, and the voltage stabilization control module and the control system are both connected with a retired battery pack module; the classified electrolytic cell comprises electrodes and electrolyte, the decommissioned battery pack module is connected with the electrodes to supply power to the classified electrolytic cell, and the output power of the decommissioned battery pack module is controlled to be equal to the rated power of the classified electrolytic cell through the control system; the hydrogen storage module comprises a purification and pressurization module and a hydrogen storage tank, the purification and pressurization module is connected with a gas outlet of the classification electrolytic tank, and hydrogen generated by electrolytic hydrogen production of the classification electrolytic tank is sequentially purified, dried and pressurized through the purification and pressurization module and then stored in the hydrogen storage tank. According to the invention, the retired power battery can be fully recycled, and the efficiency of hydrogen production by electrolysis of water is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种太阳能联合退役电池再利用的制氢系统，包括太阳供电系统、分类电解槽和储氢模块；太阳供电系统包括太阳能光伏电池模块，太阳能光伏电池模块与稳压控制模块相连，稳压控制模块和控制系统均与退役电池组模块相连；分类电解槽包括电极和电解液，退役电池组模块与电极相连从而为分类电解槽供电，通过控制系统控制退役电池组模块的输出功率与分类电解槽的额定功率相等；储氢模块包括纯化加压模块和氢气储罐，纯化加压模块与分类电解槽的出气口连接，分类电解槽电解制氢生成的氢气经过纯化加压模块依次纯化、干燥和加压后，存储至氢气储罐。本发明能够充分回收利用退役动力电池，并提高了电解水制氢的效率。"
                }
            ]
